milestones.description: Fraser Watts and Majid Haq's 103-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 99 between Fraser Watts and Majid Haq
Scotland's 78-run win against Kenya is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 7-run win against Canada
This is the lowest match aggregate (431) involving teams Kenya & Scotland in ODIs
Hamilton has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Neil McCallum's 5
Fraser Watts has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Hamilton's record
